        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Raspberry PI</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.raspberrypi.org/">The Raspberry PI Organization</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.raspberrypi.org/products/raspberry-pi-3-model-b/">The Raspberry PI 3 Model B</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/iot-core/getstarted">Microsoft Windows IoT Core</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
